{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":50779,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"关键在于不知道嘲讽的是阵营（哪一方）还是个体（哪个人），也不知道因为什么而嘲讽","timestamp":1593234125,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50780,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这种行为就和懂得都懂差不多","timestamp":1593234143,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50785,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 是啊是啊，这就从讨论沦为对喷了","timestamp":1593234163,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50844,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"其实就算是喷，也应该针对话题喷，而不是人身攻击","timestamp":1593234832,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50859,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这种事情见得多了，我只想说懂得都懂，不懂的我也不多解释，毕竟自己知道就好，细细品吧。你们也别来问我怎么了，利益牵扯太大，说了对你我都没好处，当不知道就行了，其余的我只能说这里面水很深，牵扯到很多东西。详细情况你们自己是很难找的，网上大部分已经删除干净了，所以我只能说懂得都懂。\n（狗头保命）","timestamp":1593234958,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50887,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 这种事还不好管，删帖都不好制定标准。但要是不管，树洞就微博化了。建议管理员弄点啥规定。","timestamp":1593235184,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50895,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 可操作性强的规定基本不可能有啊……","timestamp":1593235259,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50933,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 唉是啊","timestamp":1593235504,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":50950,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"但也应该能做点什么吧，比如（我瞎想的）可以把每一次举报的理由都反馈给被举报者？\n至少得让被举报的人知道，他的行为不受欢迎吧","timestamp":1593235650,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":51046,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 可是现在连举报评论功能都没有呢","timestamp":1593236240,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":51082,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":8481,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 别指望了，这树洞就只是一个T大同学匿名的精神溺便器而已。","timestamp":1593236435,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":1,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":8481,"reply":11,"tag":null,"text":"#8465\n我觉得这一串树洞，和咱们以后的树洞，都做到把自己的观点表达清楚好吧。。。而且少点戾气\n自己要说什么都不说清楚就上来嘲讽，这样的风气让谁都没法好好讨论。","timestamp":1593234053,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}